âœ… Step-by-Step Guide to Learn Pattern Identification:
1. Learn Problem Categories First (DSA Topics = Patterns)
Har topic ek pattern ke group jaisa hota hai:

Pattern / Topic	Common Problems
Sliding Window	Max sum subarray, Anagrams in string
Two Pointers	Pair sum, Triplet sum, Sorted array merge
Stack	Next Greater Element, Valid Parentheses
Binary Search	Search in Rotated Array, Koko Eating Bananas
Recursion + Backtrack	N-Queens, Subsets, Permutations
Dynamic Programming	Knapsack, Fibonacci, LIS

2. Learn by Solving Pattern-Based Sets
