3 problems same logic se solve karte ho...

Tumhara brain recognize kar leta hai: "Acha, yeh pattern toh pehle kiya hai!"

3. Maintain a Pattern Notebook or Digital Sheet
Har baar jab tum ek naye pattern ka question solve karo:

ğŸ“ Note down:

Problem name

Pattern used (e.g. "Stack â€“ NGE")

Key idea / dry run

Time complexity

Isse tumhara pattern recall strong banega interview time par.

4. Dry Run Multiple Examples
Dry run karne se:

Tum logic nahi bhoolte

Tum dekh paate ho: "Yeh pattern fit ho raha hai ya nahi"

5. Ask Yourself These Questions for Every Problem
Input sorted hai? â†’ Binary Search ya Two pointers?

